📲 Step 3 - ADB Setup (Phone Control)
Enable ADB on your phone:


Settings → About Phone → tap Build Number 7 times
Settings → Developer Options → USB Debugging → ON


Then on your PC:


# Install ADB
# Windows: download from https://developer.android.com/tools/releases/platform-tools
# Mac/Linux:
brew install android-platform-tools   # Mac
sudo apt install adb                  # Linux

# Connect phone via USB, then verify:
adb devices
# You should see your device listed
